    Builder<MessageFiller>

    public class MessageFillerBuilder
extends Object

    Builder that help construct the message fillers. The aim of a message filler is to generate some values to put into the message object.

      • withSubjectFiller

        public MessageFillerBuilder withSubjectFiller()
        Enable the generation of subject of the message. The subject can automatically be extracted from the content:
        • If content of the message is HTML, then the title is used as subject
        • If content of the message is text and the first line starts with "Subject:", then it is used as subject

        Automatically called by useDefaults(String...) and useDefaults(Properties, String...)

        Returns:
        this instance for fluent use
